data.value: Tarte tatin, which emerged as a result of a mistake made by Stephanie Tatin in 1898, is one of the most popular apples of France today. Stephanie Tatin, trying to make a traditional taste of the apples from the hands of sugar and oil is falling into the hands. Trying to save the dessert in a hurry, Tatin adds the tart dough over the burning fruits and places them in the pot. After this stage, the famous apple pie is also revealed. Almost every other person who likes this sweet is a must-have for all those who go to France. After a nice meal, you should definitely try this dessert with tea or coffee.
